postReview.title: Fulham 2-1 Nottingham Forest: Bassey header downs high-flying visitors
postReview.description: Calvin Bassey and Emile Smith Rowe scored with headers as Fulham did a double over Nottingham Forest with a 2-1 victory at Craven Cottage.

preReview.title: Silva excited by healthy competition between Jimenez and Muniz
